g.text: - Riders could be able to get a fare estimate based on pickup and dropoff location
- Riders could be able to send a request based on the fare estimate, then wait for the matching process
- Drivers could be able to get a notification and then decide to whether accept or deny the request
- Scalability: the system could be able to handle peak-hours and burst during some special events
- Low-latency: the system could be able to complete the rider-driver matching less than 1 min
- Match the ride to the driver
